{
  "texts": [
    "To address these issues, our study has developed an innovative multimodal emotion recognition method that combines tensor decomposition fusion with self-supervised multi-task learning.",
    "The main innovations and contributions of our study are as follows:• Introduction of Tucker Decomposition: To tackle the large parameter issue inherent in traditional tensor fusion, we employed Tucker decomposition technology, effectively reducing the model parameters and thus lowering the risk of overfitting.",
    "• Construction of a Multi-task Learning Mechanism: Addressing the limitation of single annotation, we introduced the concept of label generation.",
    "By constructing a learning mechanism for both multimodal and unimodal tasks, our method captures the emotional differences between modalities more precisely.• Extensive experiments and analyses were conducted on public datasets such as CMU-MOSI and CMU-MOSEI.",
    "The results demonstrate that our method significantly outperforms existing methods in terms of performance.We have made the related code open source."
  ]
}